## Limitations

The findings are based on publicly available articles and discussions, which may not cover all perspectives or the latest data on the topic. Additionally, the opinions expressed in these sources may be subjective and not representative of the broader business community. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the need for entrepreneurs versus managers.